          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Constructed with durable materials, Nextable ensures long-lasting. Smooth-rolling casters allow hassle-free movement across spaces, enabling quick reconfiguration. Its sturdy build blends function and convenience, making it a reliable addition to any workspace."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "The tabletop flips smoothly, allowing multiple tables to nest compactly. This makes storage efficient and setup quick for dynamic training or meeting spaces."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Equipped with high-quality wheels, the table moves easily across rooms and locks securely in place. Ideal for flexible layouts and frequent reconfigurations."
